"'''Play Me Like You Play Your Guitar'''" is a song written by [[Keith Potger]] and [[Tony Macaulay]] and performed by [[Duane Eddy]], with vocals by the Rebelettes. The song reached #9 on the [[UK Singles Chart]] in 1975.<ref>[http://www.musicvf.com/song.php?title=Play+Me+Like+You+Play+Your+Guitar+by+Duane+Eddy&id=13121 Duane Eddy, "Play Me Like You Play Your Guitar" Chart Positions] Retrieved April 29, 2014</ref>

The song was produced by [[Tony Macaulay]].<ref>[http://www.45cat.com/record/gt11 Duane Eddy, "Play Me Like You Play Your Guitar" single release] Retrieved April 29, 2014</ref>

